    <!-- 
        TICKETMASTER API KEY CONFIGURATION
        ==================================
        To use the Ticketmaster Discovery API, you need an API key:
        
        1. Visit https://developer.ticketmaster.com/
        2. Sign up for a free account or log in
        3. Go to "Apps" > "Create a new app"
        4. Fill in the app details:
           - App Name: LocalPulse
           - Description: Android event discovery app
           - URL: http://localhost (or your website)
        5. Click "Save" and copy your Consumer Key (API Key)
        6. Replace YOUR_TICKETMASTER_API_KEY_HERE below with your actual key
        
        Example:
        <string name="ticketmaster_api_key">abc123xyz456YourApiKeyHere</string>
        
        Rate Limit: 5000 requests per day (free tier)
        
        Important: Keep this key secure. Do not share it publicly or commit it to version control
        if your repository is public. Consider using local.properties or environment variables
        for production apps.
    -->
